        "x": 0,
        "y": 44
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "void-keys metrics expose `userId` only; key identity collapses into user. Per-key drill-down requires VKE-side counter relabeling \u2014 out of HMB-21 scope."
      }
    },
